      "paper_id": "PMC12775414",
      "text_span_id": "bio_interp_1",
      "text": "For leukemia, the 17-gene signature includes well-characterized hematopoietic markers such as J04794 (myeloperoxidase, MPO), a key enzyme in myeloid cells that serves as a standard immunohistochemical marker for acute myeloid leukemia (AML).",
      "confidence": 0.95,
